{"id": "1469099423110791319", "channel_id": "1468237146061279356", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果是要刻意使用「扮演死者的活人」的話那當然就不該改 古籍是這樣寫不能等於他現在應該這樣寫啊== 而且我上面也說了尸位素餐正確啊", "timestamp": "2026-02-05T22:36:37.017000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-05T22:38:11.350000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1468237146061279356", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "謂之「尸解」而登仙", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1469100664603807907", "channel_id": "1468237146061279356", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "我傳的不就是教育部那邊顯示尸解嗎", "timestamp": "2026-02-05T22:41:33.012000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["259018461458595850"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1469099423110791319", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1468237146061279356", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "謂之「尸解」而登仙", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1469101543277072445", "channel_id": "1468237146061279356", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "即使到了現代沒有改變，真要認真說這是歸類在宗教用語所以不太有變化", "timestamp": "2026-02-05T22:45:02.504000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1468237146061279356", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "謂之「尸解」而登仙", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1469103635051970692", "channel_id": "1468237146061279356", "type": 19, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "我的意思是\n「教育部這樣用」是他是正確用法的原因\n但「古籍這樣寫」不是他是正確用法的原因\n結論是一樣的 但過程不同 即便同意結論 我認為精準區分過程是有必要的", "timestamp": "2026-02-05T22:53:21.222000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-05T22:55:54.068000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1469100664603807907", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1468237146061279356", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "謂之「尸解」而登仙", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1469104154243895543", "channel_id": "1468237146061279356", "type": 0, "author_id": "259018461458595850", "author_name": "amstelredam", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果「古籍是這樣寫」就可以獨立成為某種寫法正確的條件，那很多錯字都會變成「正確」的，這個理由顯然不充分\n當然，教育部怎麼定義算是一個權力問題，在比較差的狀況下，教育部隨便定義就會導致「教育部說這是對的」也沒辦法成為充分理由，這我不否認", "timestamp": "2026-02-05T22:55:25.007000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1468237146061279356", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "謂之「尸解」而登仙", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
